are the links that lead to it.
Chapter 9: Best Practices & Performance
By now, you’ve seen scripts grow from tiny triggers to dynamic lorebooks. That’s powerful — but it also
means there’s more room for mistakes. This chapter teaches you how to keep scripts:
Safe (they don’t crash)
